    <title>Here Comes Mr. Jordan</title>
      <minor />
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{infobox film|
name=Here Comes Mr. Jordan|
director=[Alexander Hall]|
writer=[Harry Segall] (play ''Heaven Can Wait'')<br>[Sidney Buchman]<br>[Seton I. Miller]|
producer=[Everett Riskin]|
starring=[Robert Montgomery]<br>[Evelyn Keyes]<br>[Claude Rains]<br>[Rita Johnson]<br>[Edward Everett Horton]|
distributor=[Columbia Pictures]|
released=[23 July], [1941]|
